data.description: PRICE IMPROVEMENT!!! FULLY RENOVATED 2 BEDROOM 2 BATH HOME ON A FENCED IN LOT! The upgrades in this home are endless. Walk thru the front door and the 1st thing you’ll notice is the gorgeous custom wood panel ceilings with in set lighting. Brand new kitchen features stainless steel appliances, oversized cabinets with a built in pantry, deep under mount sink with retractable faucet, upgraded backsplash & custom hardwood butcher block counters. The master bathroom features an upgraded vanity, custom tiled shower with a retractable shower head & an overhead, oversized roan shower head. The main bathroom features custom tiled walls and upgraded vanity. Brand new LVP flooring, fresh paint, new windows and new blinds throughout, new refrigerator, new washer and dryer, new Nest thermostats with Smart door lock and smart lights. Metal roof, AC & water heater. Private fenced in parking for 2 vehicles. Schedule your showing today!!
